===Etymology 1===
From {{inh|en|enm|-ite}}, from {{der|en|fro|-ite}}, {{m|fro|-ete}}, {{m|fro|-eteit||-ity}}, from {{der|en|la|-itƒÅtem}}, from {{m|la|-itƒÅs}}, from {{der|en|ine-pro|*-it-|pos=suffix}}. Cognate with {{cog|got|-êåπêå∏êå∞||-th}}, {{cog|goh|-ida||-th}}, {{cog|ang|-√æo}}, {{m|ang|-√æu}}, {{m|ang|-√æ||-th}}. More at {{l|en|-th}}.

