# {{lb|en|auxiliary}} {{non-gloss definition|A [[syntactic]] [[marker]].}}
## {{lb|en|auxiliary}} {{non-gloss definition|A [[syntactic]] [[marker]] in a [[question]] whose main verb is not another auxiliary verb or {{m-lite|en|be}}.}}
