From {{inh|en|enm|eye}}, {{m|enm|eie}}, {{m|enm|y√´}}, {{m|enm|eighe}}, {{m|enm|eyghe}}, {{m|enm|y»ùe}}, {{m|enm|ey»ùe}}, from {{inh|en|ang|ƒìage|t=eye}}, from {{inh|en|gmw-pro|*augƒÅ}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*aug√¥|t=eye}} (compare {{cog|sco|ee}}, {{cog|fy|each}}, {{cog|nl|oog}}, {{cog|de|Auge}}, {{cog|da|√∏je}}, {{cog|nb|√∏ye}}, {{cog|nn|auga}}, {{cog|sv|√∂ga}}), from {{der|en|ine-pro|*h‚ÇÉok ∑-}}, {{m|ine-pro|*h‚ÇÉek ∑-|t=eye; to see}}.

