#*: He was about to roar when, lying among the black sticks and straw under the cliff, he saw a whole '''skull'''‚Äîperhaps a cow's '''skull''', a '''skull''', perhaps, with the teeth in it. Sobbing, but absent-mindedly, he ran farther and farther away until he held the '''skull''' in his arms.
# These bones as a symbol for [[death]]; [[death's-head]].
# {{lb|en|figuratively}} The [[mind]] or [[brain]].
